---
title: Beetroot Relish-Glazed-Chicken  with Garlic Crushed Veggies & Celery Slaw
description: If you’re looking for ‘wow factor’ then you’re going to want a pop of colour on your chicken and nothing can beat
the beetroot when it comes to vibrancy on a plate. Glaze the chicken in a sweet beetroot relish to shine beside the
fragrant garlic crushed veggies for a dinner that tastes as good as it looks.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
